{"tid":616992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呢架踢街場d人嗲係咪咁無品呀？","createTime":"2018-04-04T15:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T14:36:25.000Z","uid":102240,"like":4,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"3d37031df855988c1c0600c1daf7b85cc5c73d29","tid":616992,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"香港街場生態真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫條仔約波搞7打7，臨尾兩日佢話唔夠人5打5，fine借人比你，點知一開波就想打交...<br />\n<br />\n對面係咁鏟，人過又唔比波過，大佬你踄英超唔好，包你做motm呢期，到半場埋去講數話斯文d，傾唔埋爛，成班粗口爛舌勁有火藥味，不過我地呢邊呢度都有人燥，打和算啦呢度，到再踢又係鏟過，衰到自己人鏟自己人，我地問對面「再踢人不如打交」，點知佢話係你地自鏟關我咩事，勁串嘴，唔係你辣著火頭點會搞到場波咁，最後臨熄燈隊長打副隊長，人地幫手報警，實際係報仇<br />\n<br />\n根本成個街場風氣都係波牛搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec85f5765907d8074b0e7b8d3b04808b5099660","tid":616992,"uid":74898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"同mk仔踢波預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cecc14a1b8e989aa188b21dc151206696cc93c","tid":616992,"uid":102240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ec85f5765907d8074b0e7b8d3b04808b5099660","tid":616992,"uid":74898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"同mk仔踢波預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2056431fa4aa787fc609996751f5d5909056315a","tid":616992,"uid":177089,"like":60,"dislike":14,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"踢波根本係廢青活動<br />\n中年踢唔郁就賭波 睇下波台就知<br />\n成班社會垃圾"},{"pid":"5755ecee0f43768ff1f7867c11e16037d50fcd8c","tid":616992,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2056431fa4aa787fc609996751f5d5909056315a","tid":616992,"uid":177089,"like":60,"dislike":14,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:53:33.000Z","m